Grammy-nominated producer and pop artist, Sophie is dead. The Los-Angeles-based artist died at age 34 on Saturday after she slipped and fell off while watching the full moon. SOPHIE’s rep announced the news of her death in a statement released on Saturday. Part of the statement read: “It is with profound sadness that we inform you that musician and producer SOPHIE passed away this morning around 4am in Athens following a sudden accident. “Sophie, true to her spirituality, had climbed up to watch the full moon and accidentally slipped and fell. “ The family thanked everyone for their love and support and “request privacy during this devastating time.”